ton nks_cc_trigger_element nks_toggle_tab_1\" href=\"#\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-684\" src=\"https:www.teleqwest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Request-a-Free-Quote-Teleqwest-300x60.png\" alt=\"Request-a-Free-Quote-Teleqwest\" width=\"300\" height=\"60\" /></a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"4\" full_width_row=\"true\" bg_cover=\"true\" bg_attachment=\"true\"][vc_column animation=\"fadeIn\" css=\".vc_custom_1463789274748{padding-top: 200px !important;padding-bottom: 200px !important;background-image: url(https:www.teleqwest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/pexels-photo.jpg?id=977) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\n<blockquote>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">The Internet has changed everything. We expect to know everything instantly. If you don\'t understand digital communication, you\'re at a disadvantage.\n- Bob Parsons</h1>\n</blockquote>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row margin_top=\"50\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\" animation=\"fadeInLeft\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3><span style=\"color: #2ecc71;\"><b>High Speed Internet For Your Business.</b></span></h3>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\" animation=\"fadeInRight\"][vc_column_text]As an authorized Dealer for some of the worlds most reliable high speed internet providers, TeleQwest can offer incredible and reliable high speed internet options for your business. Its a business tool that makes your business more productive, and efficient. We make those important files download quicker, so you can get to business faster up to 5x faster than slow DSL in fact. We also provide value added features like Business WiFi, no data caps, and access to additional productivity tools that meet your business needs to help you run even more efficiently.\n<div></div>\nWe provide Internet services to meet the needs of a range of businesses from small business to enterprise. So put TeleQwest to work for your business and unlock a new stream of productivity  just choose from a variety of speeds that suit your business needs. Then let your business take advantage of all the benefits that come with better, faster Internet, including:\n<ul>\n	<li>Fast Internet speeds  Customers and guests can download, email and stream at the high speeds theyve come to expect.</li>\n	<li>Limitless Connection  has no caps, so you can upload/download and access however much you want.</li>\n	<li>Wireless Connectivity  Business WiFi gives employees, customers, and guests access to what is important to them  its also included on all Deluxe plans or higher.</li>\n	<li>Access Additional Services  Once you upgrade your Internet, customize the service to meet any number of needs with our many add-ons  like web hosting, Internet for telecommuters, and more!</li>\n</ul>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\" animation=\"fadeInLeft\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3><span style=\"color: #2ecc71;\"><strong>Data Handling </strong></span></h3>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\" animation=\"fadeInRight\"][vc_column_text]Different businesses have different data needs, some send a few emails and some upload large videos. That is why Comcast provides no data limits, our plans are separated by the speed that you need.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/4\" animation=\"fadeInLeft\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3><span style=\"color: #2ecc71;\"><strong>Day-to-day tasks</strong></span></h3>\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"3/4\" animation=\"fadeInRight\"][vc_column_text]Having the right Internet plan means being equipped to handle your businesss important tasks  whether youre sending menus off to the printer, sharing a big presentation with your team, or offering guests a speedy pipeline to access whats important to them. Having the right Internet plan for your business makes your business more productive and your employees and customers will take notice.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"4\" margin_bottom=\"-50\" full_width_row=\"true\" padding_left=\"300\" padding_right=\"300\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" bg_color=\"#2ecc71\" css=\".vc_custom_1463470406993{background-color: #2ecc71 !important;}\"][vc_column animation=\"fadeInDown\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3 class=\"block-title\" style=\"text-align: center;\">It\'s worth a conversation to set your business apart.</h3>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]<a class=\"my_theme_standard_button nks_cc_trigger_element nks_toggle_tab_2\" href=\"#\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-870\" src=\"https:www.teleqwest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Landing-Buttons-Dark-300x37.png\" alt=\"Landing-Buttons-Dark\" width=\"300\" height=\"37\" /></a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]<a href=\"https:www.teleqwest.com/communication-services/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-871\" src=\"https:www.teleqwest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Landing-Buttons-Dark-Learn-More-300x37.png\" alt=\"Landing-Buttons-Dark-Learn-More\" width=\"300\" height=\"37\" /></a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]\";}s:24:\"mini-services_1807668820\";a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:13:\"Mini Services\";s:8:\"template\";s:6805:\"[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" full_height=\"yes\" equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" parallax=\"content-moving\" parallax_image=\"862\" animation=\"fadeInLeft\" margin_top=\"-50\" parallax_content=\"parallax_content_value\" parallax_content_sense=\"0.5\" anchor=\"business-phone\" el_id=\"business-phone\" css=\".vc_custom_1463910787376{background-image: url(https:www.teleqwest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/stock-photo-1097645212.png?id=) !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1463910570864{padding-top: 30px !important;}\"]\n<h3>Business Phone</h3>\nIts time to step it up. Get rid of the garbled, jittery phone calls running over the public Internet.Thanks to our partnerships with the nations top business phone providers, TeleQwest cangive you reliable, crystal-clear, IP-based voice service with the quality of landline phones  and we caninstall it for you, train your employees and provide easy online tools for you to manage your system if you request.\n\nOur Business Voice Mobility links your business phone to your mobile devices so youre always connected. You simply download the Business Voice Mobility App and go.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1463909427104{padding-top: 30px !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: contain !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"2\" padding_top=\"30\" anchor=\"high-speed-internet\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>High Speed Internet</h3>\nGet Nationwide, Business-class high-speed Internet with Guaranteed bandwidth from 1.5 Mbps to 100G.\n\nWhether youre a small business or a multi-location enterprise, TeleQwesthas scalable, customized solutions to meet your unique needs.\nAs an authorized Dealer for some of the worlds most reliable high speed internet providers, TeleQwest can offer incredible and reliable high speed internet options for your business. Its a business tool that makes your business more productive, and efficient. We make those important files download quicker, so you can get to business faster up to 5x faster than slow DSL in fact. We also provide value added features like Business WiFi, no data caps, and access to additional productivity tools that meet your business needs to help you run even more efficiently.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row margin_top=\"30\" anchor=\"voip\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>VoIP</h3>\nWe have helpful and knowledgeable staff to assist you through your VoIP Business experience. Our Sales team works hard to set you up with the right system, the Customer Care department is available to guide you through account set-up and any troubleshooting, and our Engineering team is constantly improving and innovating features to make your service even better.\n\nYouve heard of the Cloud and why its an amazing solution at an affordable price, well, let us explain why.\n\nWhen you move to the Cloud, youve got 40+ built-in calling features enabling your business to do more. And thanks to the variousVoIP providers we work with,features are hosted in the cloud instead of your closet. Thats just smart business, no matter what your size.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"2\" padding_top=\"30\" anchor=\"credit-card-processing\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>Credit Card Processing</h3>\nWe provide and support a wide array of terminal and software options, including the latest mobile solutions. We are experts at accommodating existing systems with easegiving you the support that you need to be successful at what you do regardless of your current situation\n\nAccept credit card payments anywhere! Well get you set up with the latest mobile processing solutions so you can best serve your customers. We have solutions that can integrate with existing POS software, allowing you to accept credit card payments using your iPhone, iPad, tablets, or any other mobile device. Whatever your situation, we will find you the solution that best fits your business.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row margin_top=\"30\" anchor=\"crm-integration\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>CRM Integration</h3>\nDo you spend more time juggling between sales activities? There is a better way to follow up your routine sales tasks, appointments and calls. With a CRM, you can now sell faster by focusing on the prospects that are most important for you today.Make adding clients to your roster more about building a relationship rather then stressing if your deadlines are going to be met.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"2\" padding_top=\"30\" anchor=\"lead-generation\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text]\n<h3>Lead Generation</h3>\nOn average, TeleQwesthelps our customers boost their sales by 37%. But the benefits of TeleQwestfor business dont end when you make a sale. Customer service benefits, too. Our solutions help to build stronger relationships with your current customers, win new ones, and accelerate business growth. And intelligent marketing automation helps you focus resources on the tasks that really add value, while a common platform for all your data helps to build strong relationships across all your channels, including social, Web, email, and customer call centers.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=\"4\" margin_bottom=\"-50\" full_width_row=\"true\" padding_left=\"300\" padding_right=\"300\" padding_top=\"50\" padding_bottom=\"50\" bg_color=\"#2ecc71\" css=\".vc_custom_1463909065710{background-color: #2ecc71 !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_column_text]\n<h3 class=\"block-title\" style=\"text-align: center;\">It\'s worth a conversation to set your business apart.</h3>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]<a class=\"my_theme_standard_button nks_cc_trigger_element nks_toggle_tab_2\" href=\"#\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-870\" src=\"https:www.teleqwest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Landing-Buttons-Dark-300x37.png\" alt=\"Landing-Buttons-Dark\" width=\"300\" height=\"37\" /></a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][vc_column_text]<a href=\"https:www.teleqwest.com/communication-services/\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-871\" src=\"https:www.teleqwest.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Landing-Buttons-Dark-Learn-More-300x37.png\" alt=\"Landing-Buttons-Dark-Learn-More\" width=\"300\" height=\"37\" /></a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]\";}}','no'),(25242,'wp-emmet','a:8:{s:14:\"use_codemirror\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"profile\";s:4:\"html\";s:8:\"textarea\";a:2:{s:9:\"variables\";a:1:{s:11:\"indentation\";s:1:\"	\";}s:7:\"options\";a:3:{s:6:\"syntax\";s:4:\"html\";s:7:\"use_tab\";s:1:\"1\";s:12:\"pretty_break\";s:1:\"1\";}}s:10:\"codemirror\";a:7:{s:5:\"theme\";s:7:\"default\";s:14:\"indentWithTabs\";s:1:\"1\";s:10:\"indentUnit\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"tabSize\";s:1:\"4\";s:11:\"smartIndent\";s:1:\"1\";s:12:\"lineWrapping\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"lineNumbers\";s:1:\"1\";}s:16:\"codemirror_style\";s:111:\"font-family: Ricty, \"VL Gothic\", monospace, sans-serif;\nfont-size: 16px;\nline-height: 1.3;\nletter-spacing: 1px;\";s:5:\"scope\";a:4:{s:4:\"post\";s:1:\"1\";s:12:\"theme-editor\";s:1:\"1\";s:13:\"plugin-editor\";s:1:\"1\";s:6:\"others\";s:1:\"1\";}s:18:\"override_shortcuts\";s:0:\"\";s:9:\"shortcuts\";a:22:{s:19:\"Expand Abbreviation\";s:6:\"Meta+E\";s:18:\"Match Pair Outward\";s:6:\"Meta+D\";s:17:\"Match Pair Inward\";s:12:\"Shift+Meta+D\";s:13:\"Matching Pair\";s:6:\"Meta+T\";s:22:\"Wrap with Abbreviation\";s:12:\"Shift+Meta+A\";s:15:\"Next Edit Point\";s:14:\"Ctrl+Alt+Right\";s:15:\"Prev Edit Point\";s:13:\"Ctrl+Alt+Left\";s:11:\"Select Line\";s:6:\"Meta+L\";s:11:\"Merge Lines\";s:12:\"Meta+Shift+M\";s:14:\"Toggle Comment\";s:6:\"Meta+/\";s:14:\"Split/Join Tag\";s:6:\"Meta+J\";s:10:\"Remove Tag\";s:6:\"Meta+K\";s:24:\"Evaluate Math Expression\";s:12:\"Shift+Meta+Y\";s:21:\"Increment number by 1\";s:7:\"Ctrl+Up\";s:21:\"Decrement number by 1\";s:9:\"Ctrl+Down\";s:23:\"Increment 